de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.measurement.kieker

Class CodeSectionIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.measurement.kieker.CodeSectionIdentifier

  • public class CodeSectionIdentifier
extends Object
    Resolves code sections to unique IDs and back. Equal code sections are assigned to the same identifier, different code sections are assigned to different identifiers. Identifiers obtained through getIdOf(CodeSection) are only valid for the same Identifier instance.

    This class is thread safe.
